will receive this...

272
00:16:25,833 --> 00:16:26,791
But please...

273
00:16:26,875 --> 00:16:28,083
Do your best.

274
00:16:52,791 --> 00:16:53,833
Mai!

275
00:16:53,916 --> 00:16:56,500
[MIKOTO growls]

276
00:16:56,583 --> 00:16:58,208
Searrs Corporation?

277
00:16:58,291 --> 00:16:59,750
[NATSUKI]
It's a mysterious corporation

278
00:16:59,833 --> 00:17:01,750
that hides in the shadows
of a giant conglomerate

279
00:17:01,833 --> 00:17:02,916
based in the West.

280
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:04,791
