283
00:17:08,666 --> 00:17:11,083
[MAi, NATSUKI gasp]

284
00:17:11,166 --> 00:17:13,083
[MIYU] We do much more
than merely control

285
00:17:13,166 --> 00:17:14,416
the fate of world leaders.

286
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:16,333
We've been instrumental
in determining the fate

287
00:17:16,416 --> 00:17:18,500
of the world since
ancient times.

288
00:17:18,583 --> 00:17:22,000
And it's all in order to
usher in the Golden Age.

289
00:17:22,083 --> 00:17:22,791
Miyu?

290
00:17:22,875 --> 00:17:25,333
And... Alyssa?!

291
00:17:25,416 --> 00:17:26,625
[NATSUKI]
It's you!

292
00:17:26,708 --> 00:17:28,083
[MAI]
Why?

293
00:17:28,166 --> 00:17:29,791
This can't be happening!

294
00:17:29,875 --> 00:17:31,458
Miyu? Alyssa?!

295
00:17:31,541 --> 00:17:33,041
[ALYSSA]
Hmph. Miyu?

296
00:17:33,125 --> 00:17:34,166
[MIYU]
Yes.

297
00:17:36,125 --> 00:17:37,166
[BOTH gasp]

298
00:17:43,125 --> 00:17:45,958
[MIYU] Confirming the genetic
imprint of Alyssa Searrs.

299
00:17:46,041 --> 00:17:47,458
Rebooting in Mode D.

300
00:17:47,541 --> 00:17:51,250
Canceling restrictions
numbers 4 through 12.

301
00:17:51,333 --> 00:17:53,833
[MIKOTO growls]

302
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:55,666
[MIKOTO grunts]

303
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:57,500
[BAT BEAST roars]

304
00:17:57,583 --> 00:17:59,500
Well, Miyu, good luck.

305
00:17:59,583 --> 00:18:00,916
I'll do my best.

306
00:18:06,458 --> 00:18:08,500
[gasps]

307
00:18:08,583 --> 00:18:09,625
[NATSUKI grunts]

308
00:18:11,875 --> 00:18:12,875
[NATSUKI]
Ugh!

309
00:18:15,708 --> 00:18:16,708
Duran!

310
00:18:21,625 --> 00:18:23,208
[NATSUKI]
Load Chrome Cartridge!

311
00:18:24,333 --> 00:18:25,500
Fire!

312
00:18:33,875 --> 00:18:34,875
[MAI, NATSUKI scream]

313
00:18:36,708 --> 00:18:37,791
Mai!

314
00:18:40,333 --> 00:18:41,166
[DURAN yelps]

315
00:18:41,250 --> 00:18:42,375
Duran!

316
00:18:42,458 --> 00:18:43,500
[MIKOTO yells]

317
00:18:46,583 --> 00:18:47,750
[MIKOTO growls]

318
00:18:49,041 --> 00:18:50,708
[MIKOTO screams]

319
00:18:50,791 --> 00:18:51,791
Mikoto!

320
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:58,708
[BAT BEAST growls]

321
00:18:58,791 --> 00:18:59,958
Mikoto!

322
00:19:04,458 --> 00:19:05,708
[MAI]
Kagutsuchi!

323
00:19:12,208 --> 00:19:13,250
[MIKOTO grunts]

324
00:19:17,916 --> 00:19:18,750
[MAI]
Mikoto!

325
00:19:18,833 --> 00:19:20,625
Mai! Are you all right?

326
00:19:47,208 --> 00:19:48,750
[MIYU] That's quite
an incredible power.

327
00:19:48,833 --> 00:19:49,875
[BOTH gasp]

328
00:20:02,791 --> 00:20:03,916
Mai! Do it!

329
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:04,750
Fire!

330
00:20:04,833 --> 00:20:06,166
[MAI grunts]

331
00:20:12,833 --> 00:20:16,750
[MIYU] Miss Tokiha, you are
a very interesting person.

332
00:20:16,833 --> 00:20:18,625
We will meet again.

333
00:20:18,708 --> 00:20:19,958
Oh, no, ya don't!

334
00:20:21,333 --> 00:20:23,666
[BOTH grunt]

335
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,375
[NATSUKI groans]

336
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:44,375
What?! At Tsukimori?

337
00:20:44,458 --> 00:20:46,125
He was apparently arrested.

338
00:20:46,208 --> 00:20:48,916
A creep of a guy who liked
to call himself a vampire.

339
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,125
[SHIZURU] And he confessed to
all the crimes he committed

340
00:20:51,208 --> 00:20:52,833
--at this school.
--[HARUKA] What?!

341
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:55,583
I wonder...

342
00:20:55,666 --> 00:20:57,250
...if she did it...

343
00:21:00,875 --> 00:21:03,125
