to manage on your own.

344
00:21:03,208 --> 00:21:05,375
Father has taken full
responsibility

345
00:21:05,458 --> 00:21:08,708
for having tarnished the dignity
and reputation of the chapel.

346
00:21:08,791 --> 00:21:12,208
