who is now in control.

370
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:22,750
In order to usher in
the Golden Age.

371
00:23:56,583 --> 00:23:58,791
[SHIHO] Mai, how'd
they get to be so big?

372
00:23:58,875 --> 00:24:00,291
