375
00:24:03,625 --> 00:24:05,708
[SHIHO] Ugh! You wanna
keep it a secret?!

376
00:24:05,791 --> 00:24:07,000
You're mean!

377
00:24:07,083 --> 00:24:09,000
[CHIE] That's right!
Don't keep it to yourself!

378
00:24:09,083 --> 00:24:09,833
